+# Exploration 002 Report - Freeze The Honest Scorecard, Guardrails, And Step-2 Verdict
+
+## Goal
+
+Using the witness and authority freeze from Exploration 001, write the Step-7
+guardrail memo:
+
+- hard pass/fail gates versus secondary diagnostics;
+- no-repair rule versus closure-forced bookkeeping;
+- no-overclaim rule; and
+- whether Chain Step 2 is now well posed.
+
+## Sources Used
+
