+  the sharpest record instability is not about the witness object itself but
+  about authority precedence inside the Step-5 leakage record.
+- Computations worth doing later:
+  Step 2 should compute only exact closure-forced additions on the same ledger;
+  no extra calibration computation is needed in Step 1.
