+- `[VERIFIED]` After Step 1 the branch is not allowed to claim:
+  exact closure,
+  finite closed-system isolation,
+  class retention under honest closure,
+  exact dynamic survival on `I = [0, 1]`,
+  itinerary success,
+  stage-order success,
