+### 5. No-Overclaim Rule After Step 1
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` After Step 1 the branch is allowed to claim only that:
+  1. one witness,
+     `F_SS(1/12)`,
+     is frozen on the canonical ledger;
+  2. one authoritative scorecard is frozen, consisting only of repaired
